Sentencas: Rolled tubular solid oxide fuel cells are manufactured in a low-cost single step firing process, so the design offers reduced production cost.
Titulo: Thermal Cycling Evaluation of Rolled Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: All components are produced using a low cost tape casting method and are fired as a single unit.
Titulo: Thermal Cycling Evaluation of Rolled Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The geometry is self-supporting which removes the need for thick cell components further reducing cell cost and offering increased volumetric power densities.
Titulo: Thermal Cycling Evaluation of Rolled Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Here we present the results from some early studies on the influence of fast thermal cycling on performance characteristics.
Titulo: Thermal Cycling Evaluation of Rolled Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Thermal cycles were carried out heating and cooling at 10 degrees C min-1 between 400 and 800 degrees C. Less than 1% performance drop was calculated for the single cell and 5% drop was observed on the fourth cycle for the five cell bundle.
Titulo: Thermal Cycling Evaluation of Rolled Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
